author: Puidwen
title: Cute little guy
review: I found this set at a yard sale still sealed.  The parts are very generic in it, although lego makes good use of them.  A very easy build for the most part with some simple instructions.  I will say getting the pieces of the ornament to go back together was a bit tricky.  The main complaint is while the reminder will sit right in the ornament, at times he doesn't want to.
